title: Housefull 2
subTitle: Four men join hands to date and marry the women of their dreams by changing their identities and deceiving their prospective fathers-in-law.

title: Ram Jaane
subTitle: Ram Jaane, an orphan, grows up to be a criminal. His social worker friend tries to reform him but Ram is keener to win over his childhood love, Bela, than turning over a new leaf.

title: Shriman Shrimati
subTitle: Appalled by the numerous problems faced by middle-class families, a wealthy couple decide to forsake their luxuries and live among the common people to make a difference in society.

title: Deedar
subTitle: The marriage plans of Anand and Sapna are thwarted when it is revealed that Anand's business tycoon father had previously framed Sapna's father for a crime he did not commit.

title: Mohra
subTitle: After a journalist helps to release him from prison, a man agrees to work as a hitman for her, leading him to entangle with a battle between two drug lords.

title: Hum Aapke Dil Mein Rehte Hain
subTitle: Love begins with a marriage of convenience and stays with Megha and Vijay in the throes of separation. In a classic case of unfortunate timing, one realises it too soon, while the other is too late.

title: Vinashak
subTitle: A diligent and determined police officer is tasked with uncovering the truth behind a crooked warden involved in illicit weapon trafficking.

title: Khuda Gawah
subTitle: Badshah Khan travels to India to behead the man who killed Benazir's father and win her hand in marriage. He succeeds in his mission but is caught by Ranveer Singh, a jailor.

title: Chori Chori
subTitle: A cavalier young woman claims to be a businessman's fiancée and moves into his house. However, seizing the opportunity, the businessman plays along to make his true love jealous.

title: Chori Chori

title: Khoobsurat
subTitle: Sanju, a kind mn owes a smuggler a lot of money which puts him and Gudia, an orphan, in a trivial position. Later, he poses as an NRI in front of a family to swindle money.

title: Mandi
subTitle: Rukmini Bai runs a brothel that is visited by some of the most prominent men in the society. However, when one of the prostitutes has an illicit affair, the establishment is put at risk.

title: Thanedaar
subTitle: Orphaned and separated at a young age, two brothers grow up in opposing dimensions of society, only to cross paths years later as a policeman and a criminal.

title: Arjun
subTitle: Arjun has faced an uphill task, be it his education, career or even family life. When widespread corruption, crime and injustice take a toll on him, he decides to revolt but more betrayals await him.

title: Anjaam
subTitle: Vijay, a wealthy man, is in love with Shivani and is heartbroken when she gets married to Ashok. Unable to forget her, Vijay turns into a psychopath and tries to disrupt her marriage.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Suryavanshi
subTitle: An archaeologist digs up a secret underground palace, much to the dismay of the locals, who fear the consequences.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Twins Amit and Kishan are separated at birth. However, when their paths cross in the future, together they work their way through and strive to overcome challenges.

title: Suhaag

title: Salma Pe Dil Aagaya
subTitle: Two youngsters from warring tribes fall in love with each other. They believe their problems are over when a mediator helps their families to patch up, unaware of a man who had taken advantage of the enmity.

title: Vaada Raha...I Promise
subTitle: Duke Chawla leads a perfect life with a good job and a beautiful girlfriend. However, when he meets with an accident, his life changes forever.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Himmat
subTitle: When an Indian secret agent Abdul is killed in the line of duty, the mission is handed over to Ajay, his colleague and confidante, who decides to avenge his friend's death.

title: Bumm Bumm Bole
subTitle: An idealist elder brother lands in a dilemma after he misplaces his little sister's shoes. Unable to afford a new pair, the siblings agree to share the shoes, leading to several escapades.

title: Himmatwala
subTitle: After being humiliated by an autocratic landlord, a temple priest kills himself. Later, the priest's son returns to the village seeking revenge.

title: Ziddi
subTitle: Deva, a vigilant young man, quickly climbs amongst the ranks of criminals in his city. However, things get complicated when he is framed for the assassination attempt of the CM.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fiancé plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.
